This testcase works for Ubuntu, Xubuntu and Lubuntu. and should work for all other flavours of *buntu

Depends:

    sudo apt-get install python-autopilot libautopilot-gtk python-xlib

To run the tests

Terminal 1 :

cd ubiquity/autopilot
./run_ubiquity

Terminal 2:

cd ubiquity/autopilot

Then choose one of below

./autopilot run ubiquity_autopilot_tests.tests.test_english_default
                                              .test_nonenglish_default
                                              .test_english_lvm
                                              .test_nonenglish_lvm
                                              .test_english_encrypt_lvm
                                              .test_nonenglish_encrypt_lvm
                                              .test_custom_install
